{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/layout\/sizethatfits(proposal:subviews:cache:)"]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Layout\/sizeThatFits(proposal:subviews:cache:)"},"abstract":[{"text":"Returns the size of the composite view, given a proposed size","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and the view’s subviews.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sizeThatFits"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"proposal"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ProposedViewSize","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore16ProposedViewSizeV","text":"ProposedViewSize"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"subviews"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Self"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Layout\/Subviews","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore6LayoutP8Subviewsa","text":"Subviews"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cache"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Self"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Layout\/Cache","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore6LayoutP5CacheQa","text":"Cache"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CGSize","text":"CGSize"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A size proposal for the container. The container’s parent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view that calls this method might call the method more than once"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with different proposals to learn more about the container’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"flexibility before deciding which proposal to use for placement."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"proposal"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A collection of proxies that represent the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"views that the container arranges. You can use the proxies in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"collection to get information about the subviews as you determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"how much space the container needs to display them."}]}],"name":"subviews"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Optional storage for calculated data that you can share among"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the methods of your custom layout container. See"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Layout\/makeCache(subviews:)","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" for details."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"cache"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A size that indicates how much space the container"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"needs to arrange its subviews."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Implement this method to tell your custom layout container’s parent","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view how much space the container needs for a set of subviews, given","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a size proposal. The parent might call this method more than once","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"during a layout pass with different proposed sizes to test the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"flexibility of the container, using proposals like:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ProposedViewSize\/zero","type":"reference"},{"text":" proposal; respond with the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"layout’s minimum size.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ProposedViewSize\/infinity"},{"text":" proposal; respond with the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"layout’s maximum size.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ProposedViewSize\/unspecified","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" proposal; respond with the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layout’s ideal size."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The parent might also choose to test flexibility in one dimension at a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"time. For example, a horizontal stack might propose a fixed height and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"an infinite width, and then the same height with a zero width."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The following example calculates the size for a basic vertical stack","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that places views in a column, with no spacing between the views:","t